::Firaxis::
       He raises the Cybertronian equivalent of one eyebrow and does a quick 
backflip to land directly next to Meteara.  "Shame on you.  Do you honestly 
think I survived as long as I have as a mercenary without learning a few 
evasive maneuvers?"  He shakes his head and frowns.  "That was unworthy of 
Your Kind."
